<section class="kestrel-science-section">
  <div class="page-width">
    <div class="kestrel-science-section__grid">
      <div class="kestrel-science-section__content">
        <h2 class="kestrel-science-section__title">Why Men Lose Their Hair<br><span class="kestrel-science-section__subtitle">(And How to Fix It)</span></h2>

        <p class="kestrel-science-section__lead">Your hair loss and thinning isn't just genetics or an unavoidable part of aging. It's your hair crying for help.</p>

        <p class="kestrel-science-section__body">Every day, <strong>DHT</strong> (a hormone that blocks hair growth) weakens your follicles, while environmental damage and lack of nutrients make your hair thin, brittle, and prone to breakage.</p>

        <div class="kestrel-science-section__highlight">
          <p>But here's the good news:</p>
          <p class="kestrel-science-section__big">Weak hair can be strengthened and protected.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="kestrel-science-section__stats">
          <div class="kestrel-science-section__stat">
            <span class="kestrel-science-section__stat-num">97%</span>
            <span class="kestrel-science-section__stat-label">Saw less shedding<br>after 150 days</span>
          </div>
          <div class="kestrel-science-section__stat">
            <span class="kestrel-science-section__stat-num">73%</span>
            <span class="kestrel-science-section__stat-label">Noticed increased<br>hair density</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="kestrel-science-section__visual">
        <div class="kestrel-science-section__image">
          <img src="{{ 'hero-product.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="Kestrel Bio-Pilixin Complex" width="600" height="600" loading="lazy">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

